      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Presented in showroom condition, it boasts an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and mechanically flawless, this unit offers an unrivaled driving experience for the most discerning collector. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of professional excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
